overview: Susie is pregnant. Because of cravings, Susi asked Slamet, her husband, to hang out at a place where they were remembered when they were young. Slamet was jealous because he remembered something about Susi's ex-girlfriend. The trip wasn't interesting anymore. Susi is very sensitive because she is pregnant and Slamet always talks about her bad memories. This is a film about a married couple with memories of themselves.
title: Jalan Sepanjang Kenangan
